verbose_text: MRI including a gadolinium enhanced 3D time-of-flight MR angiography sequence [XREF_BIBR] was acquired at our institution in April 2004, and revealed hypervascular enhancing lesions in the carotid bifurcation bilaterally, consistent with carotid body tumors.
